---
import MainLayout from '../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import TedaviDoktorlari from '../../../components/TedaviDoktorlari.astro';

// SEO Title and Description
const pageTitle = "Implant Treatment | Original and Guaranteed Brands | Dental Implant Clinic A Plus";
const pageDescription = "100% original, certified Straumann, Bego, Nobel, Medentika, and Medigma implant treatments in Silivri and Catalca. Lifelong permanent solutions at the best prices.";
---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle}>
  
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/images/implant-banner.webp');"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-klinik-koyu/95 via-klinik-koyu/60 to-transparent z-0"></div> 
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl relative z-10 flex flex-col items-start text-left">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block bg-klinik-yesil text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">100% Original & Certified</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight text-white drop-shadow-2xl">
          Permanent Solution for Missing Teeth: <br/><span class="text-klinik-yesil">Implant Treatment</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-100 mb-10 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed drop-shadow-lg">
          Implant solutions with titanium roots, offering durability comparable to your natural teeth, guaranteed for life, and at A Plus standards.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-start">
        
        <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-6">What is an Implant?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            An implant is an artificial tooth root made of tissue-friendly titanium placed in the jawbone to restore the function and aesthetics of missing teeth. Today, it is the <strong>best, most natural, and longest-lasting</strong> method known in the treatment of missing teeth.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            In our clinic, surgical procedures are performed with millimetric precision through digital planning supported by 3D Tomography (Volumetric Tomography). In this way, the margin of error is reduced to zero and the recovery time is shortened to the maximum extent.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-l-4 border-klinik-yesil mb-10">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Why Should You Get an Implant?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 font-medium">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Protects Neighboring Teeth:</strong> There is no need to cut your healthy adjacent teeth as in bridge treatment.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Stops Bone Loss:</strong> Prevents jawbone melting in the area of the extracted tooth.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Natural Chewing Sensation:</strong> You can bite strongly as if it were your own tooth and eat everything comfortably.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Lifelong Use:</strong> Original and certified implants stay with you for life with good care.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-6">How is Implant Treatment Applied?</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">3D Tomography and Digital Planning</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">The thickness of your jawbone, the locations of the nerves, and bone density are examined in detail with 3D tomography. The position of the implant is planned down to the millimeter in a digital environment.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Surgical Procedure (Placement of the Implant)</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Under local anesthesia (without feeling any pain), the artificial titanium root is placed in the jawbone. In most cases, placing a single implant takes only 15-20 minutes.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Healing and Superstructure (Porcelain)</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">A waiting period of 2 to 3 months is required for the implant to fuse with the jawbone. The process is completed by placing your aesthetic porcelain or zirconium tooth on the implant that has integrated with the bone.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 sticky top-32">
          <img src="/images/implant-kutu.webp" alt="3D Implant Treatment" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-t-2xl shadow-sm" />
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-8 rounded-b-2xl shadow-xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Free Tomography & Examination</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6 text-sm">Find out for free if your bone structure is suitable for an implant with our 3D Tomography device.</p>
            
            <a href="https://wa.me/902124000013" target="_blank" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#25D366] text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors mb-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12.031 21.033c-1.56 0-3.084-.42-4.42-1.216l-.317-.189-3.284.861.876-3.203-.207-.331a9.022 9.022 0 0 1-1.378-4.755C3.301 7.155 7.215 3.24 12.031 3.24c2.33 0 4.519.907 6.166 2.555 1.648 1.648 2.556 3.837 2.556 6.167 0 4.914-3.915 8.829-8.73 8.829z" /></svg>
              Get Info via WhatsApp
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+902124000013" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-klinik-koyu text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-black transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
              Call Clinic: +90 212 400 00 13
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TedaviDoktorlari tedavi="implantlar" />

  <section class="py-24 bg-[#F8FAFC]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[40px] p-8 md:p-16 shadow-xl border border-gray-100 flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-start relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 w-64 h-64 bg-klinik-yesil/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative z-10">
                <span class="inline-block bg-klinik-turuncu text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Transparent Pricing Policy</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1E293B] leading-tight mb-6">
                    We Offer You 100% Original Certified,<br />
                    <span class="text-[#334155]">Guaranteed</span> Implants
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                    As Dental Implant Clinic A Plus Oral and Dental Health Polyclinic, we offer you Turkey's most affordable premium implant solutions with barcodes and international warranty passports.
                </p>
                
                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8 border border-gray-100">
                  <ul class="space-y-4 text-[#1E293B] font-bold text-sm md:text-base">
                      <li class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">
                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-klinik-yesil rounded-full"></span> Straumann Implant</span> 
                        <span class="text-klinik-turuncu">40.000 ₺</span>
                      </li>
                      <li class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">
                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-klinik-yesil rounded-full"></span> Nobel Biocare Implant</span> 
                        <span class="text-klinik-turuncu">30.750 ₺</span>
                      </li>
                      <li class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">
                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-klinik-yesil rounded-full"></span> Medentika Implant</span> 
                        <span class="text-klinik-turuncu">14.000 ₺</span>
                      </li>
                      <li class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">
                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-klinik-yesil rounded-full"></span> Bego Implant</span> 
                        <span class="text-klinik-turuncu">9.500 ₺</span>
                      </li>
                      <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-klinik-yesil rounded-full"></span> Medigma Implant</span> 
                        <span class="text-klinik-turuncu">7.000 ₺</span>
                      </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                
                <a href="https://wa.me/902124000013" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#212E3D] text-white pl-2 pr-8 py-2 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-black transition-all shadow-xl group">
                    <div class="bg-[#5C8AB4] p-3 rounded-lg group-hover:bg-klinik-yesil transition-colors">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    Inquire Original Implant Product
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col pt-8 lg:pt-0 relative z-10">
                {[
                    { name: 'Straumann Implant', logo: 'straumann.svg' },
                    { name: 'Nobel Biocare Implant', logo: 'nobel.svg' },
                    { name: 'Medentika Implant', logo: 'medentika.svg' },
                    { name: 'Bego Implant', logo: 'bego.svg' },
                    { name: 'Medigma Implant', logo: 'medigma.svg' }
                ].map((brand) => (
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-start gap-8 py-6 border-b border-gray-100 last:border-0 hover:bg-gray-50 px-6 rounded-xl transition-colors group">
                        <img src={`/icons/${brand.logo}`} alt={brand.name} class="h-10 md:h-12 w-28 md:w-36 object-contain grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300" />
                        <span class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-[#475569] group-hover:text-klinik-yesil transition-colors">{brand.name}</span>
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white pb-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Frequently Asked <span class="text-klinik-yesil">Questions</span></h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">What our patients wonder most about implant treatment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Is there pain during or after implant surgery?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">Since the implant procedure is performed under local anesthesia, absolutely no pain or ache is felt during the surgical operation. Slight leakages that may occur when the effect of anesthesia wears off after the procedure are easily controlled with standard painkillers prescribed by our doctor.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Is there a risk of the body rejecting the implant?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">Implants are made of tissue-friendly (biocompatible) pure titanium. It is biologically impossible for the human body to produce antigens against titanium and reject it as in heart or kidney transplants. When an original and certified product is used, the success rate is over 98%.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Can tooth extraction and implant be done on the same day?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">Yes, with this technique we call "Immediate Implant", if there is no acute infection in your jawbone and your bone structure is suitable, your implant can be placed in the same socket in a single session the moment your tooth is extracted.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-klinik-koyu text-white py-12 border-t-4 border-klinik-turuncu mt-auto">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-klinik-turuncu font-bold text-lg mb-3">Legal Notice</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          This website has been prepared solely for the purpose of informing patients, in full compliance with the Ministry of Health regulations.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 text-left md:text-right">
        <p class="mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Dental Implant Clinic A Plus</p>
        <p class="mb-1">Call Center: <span class="text-klinik-turuncu">+90 212 400 00 13</span></p>
        <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg inline-block text-left border border-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-1 text-xs">Last Updated: <span class="text-white font-bold">21.02.2026</span></p>
          <p class="text-xs">Editor: <a href="mailto:info@dentalimplanttrakya.com" class="text-klinik-turuncu hover:underline">info@dentalimplanttrakya.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <div class="h-16 md:hidden block"></div>

</MainLayout>